<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l23">vnd <expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>anſen</ex></expan> brıef dıe vns <expan>geſt<ex>ern</ex></expan> fru <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> . darinn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l24"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> geſant <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / alſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch hierinn <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> . <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l25">der ʒweyer brıef / wıe wır beſloſſen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beıden <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> auf dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l26"><expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ır ſchrıft ʒu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> daʒ ır eẅch deſt bas darnach wıſſet ʒu </ab>
